      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions replicate COU loading environment; multiple loading rates or conditions evaluated.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed per ASTM F1717 protocol at a single displacement rate (25 mm/min) and ambient temperature. Only one test condition evaluated; variation in loading rate and temperature not explored. This factor falls below the required level, representing a known gap acknowledged in the credibility assessment."
