      "rationale": "Construct stiffness: FEA mean 312 N/mm vs. experimental mean 318 N/mm (1.9% difference, E/uval=0.87). Yield force: FEA 1,240 N vs. experimental 1,198 N (3.5% difference, E/uval=1.12). Force at 40 mm: FEA 2,105 N vs. experimental 2,089 N (0.8% difference, E/uval=0.34). All QoIs within acceptance bounds."
